desc: We aim to bring the essence of Mother Nature's love - Honey to everyone in Singapore. We currently carry the PURITI Manuka Honey range. PURITI Manuka Honey is certified 100% Pure Raw Manuka Honey, with standards above industrial requirements. UMF and MGO certified. At PURITI Singapore, we only bring in the best.
